title: Atalanta 1-3 Club Brugge (2-5 agg): Teenager Talbi´s double fires Belgian side into last 16
description: Chemsdine Talbi scored an early double as Club Brugge stormed into the Champions League last-16 stage with a memorable 3-1 away victory over Atalanta securing a 5-2 aggregate triumph. title: Guardiola admits claims of City´s 1% chance was to play on Madrid minds
